'adaptive' & dune.fem & Adaptive grid view \\ \hline
'filtered' & dune.fem & \begin{tabular}{@{}l@{}}
  Filtered grid view for separated domains. Usage: \\
  subGrid = create.view("filtered", grid, filter, domainID) \end{tabular} \\ \hline
'geometry' & dune.fem & \begin{tabular}{@{}l@{}}
  Convert a coordinate function into a grid view. Usage: \\
  geometry = create.view("geometry", function) \end{tabular} \\ \hline
